The paper discusses control techniques for autonomous systems, which is a common topic in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of Markov decision processes (MDPs) and transfer entropy also suggests a focus on systems and control (cs.SY), as well as information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG).
